Before they parted , Alan made a proposal that was startling in the extreme . 
He would be at Colette's that night about twelve , he said . 
Were it known , it was the sort of exploit that disconsidered a young man for good with the more serious classes , but gave him a standing with the riotous . 
was simply an unlicensed publican , who gave suppers after eleven at night , the Edinburgh hour of closing . 
If you belonged to a club , you could get a much better supper at the same hour , and lose not a jot in public esteem . 
But if you lacked that qualification , and were an hungered , or inclined toward conviviality at unlawful hours , Colette's was your only port . 
You were very ill supplied . 
