In the face of these changes , it were impious to doubt fortune's kindness . 
The time began to draw near when his father would have returned from the office , and it would be the prodigal's cue to enter . 
He strolled westward by Albany Street , facing the sunset embers , pleased , he knew not why , to move in that cold air and indigo twilight , starred with street lamps . 
But there was one more disenchantment waiting him by the way . 
